		</div></li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 244.66666666667px"><div style="width: 244.66666666667px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 242.66666666667px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png/364px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png" decoding="async" width="243" height="200" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png/546px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/be/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png/729px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_065.png 2x" data-file-width="1106" data-file-height="911" /></a></div></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Satan (lower right) contends with Michael the Archangel over the body of Moses (<a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Bible_(World_English)/Jude" class="extiw" title="s:Bible (World English)/Jude">Jude 9</a>), <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julius_Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld" title="Julius Schnorr von Carolsfeld">Julius Schnorr von Carolsfeld</a>, 1860.
</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 249.33333333333px"><div style="width: 249.33333333333px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 247.33333333333px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png/371px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png" decoding="async" width="248" height="200" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png/556px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png/741px-Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld_Bibel_in_Bildern_1860_176.png 2x" data-file-width="1115" data-file-height="903" /></a></div></div>
			<div class="gallerytext">
<p>Jesus drives Satan (right) away in this 1860 woodcut by <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julius_Schnorr_von_Carolsfeld" title="Julius Schnorr von Carolsfeld">von Carolsfeld</a>
</p>
			</div>
		</div></li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 132px"><div style="width: 132px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 130px;"><div style="margin:0px auto;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Nuremberg_Chronicle_f_029r_3.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/Nuremberg_Chronicle_f_029r_3.png/195px-Nuremberg_Chronicle_f_029r_3.png" decoding="async" width="130" height="200" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/70/Nuremberg_Chronicle_f_029r_3.png 1.5x" data-file-width="278" data-file-height="428" /></a></div></div>
